00:22:13,433 --> 00:22:15,966
Thought I'd take Molly
ice fishing this weekend.

357
00:22:15,968 --> 00:22:17,468
Mm.

358
00:22:17,470 --> 00:22:20,371
Bring something more
than just jerky this time.

359
00:22:20,373 --> 00:22:22,506
